This paper deals with video analytics and compressive sensing, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and information theory (cs.IT). The Bayesian approach used in the paper involves probabilistic reasoning, which is a common theme in machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves optimization and signal processing, which are relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and systems and control (cs.SY).
